description: SugarSnap! is Cincinnati’s sweetest food truck ~ Specializing in award winning Gourmet Desserts. We provide desserts for any occasion, whether it be for your special day, or just because! We are available for private orders, birthday parties, showers, weddings and events. Our Gourmet Desserts include the following: Cupcakes, Cookies, Salted Caramel Brownies, Pies, Frozen Cheesecakes covered in Chocolate, Ice Cream Floats, and more exquisite sweets!
name: SugarSnap! Truck
